I '''Marion Bartoli''' ({{IPA-fr|maʁjɔ̃ baʁtɔli|pron}}; mibait 2 Octubre 1984) metung yang propesyonal a mamyalung tennis a king salukuyan yang pekamatas ranggu king Pransiya (kareng limang mamyalung a Pranses king mumunang dinalan o out of five French players in the top 100). Sinambut neng metung a manimunang singles (ing Wimbledon), pitung aliwa pa seven other titulung singles king [[Women's Tennis Association]] ampong atlung titulung doubles.<ref name="WTA_Stats">{{cite web|url=http://www.wtatour.com/page/Player/Stats/0,,12781~1007,00.html|title=wtatour.com -> Player profiles -> Marion Bartoli -> Stats|publisher=WTA|accessdate=7 January 2011}}</ref> Sinambut ya king [[2013 Wimbledon Championships]] kaybat neng meging katuki (''runner-up'') anyang [[2007 Wimbledon Championships|2007]], at semi-finalist ya king [[2011 French Open]].

Atlu ne sambut a makalukluk a no. 1 king yatu i Bartoli king kayang karera. Simbut ne i [[Justine Henin]] king semifinal ning [[2007 Wimbledon Championships]], i [[Jelena Janković]] king kapata round ning [[2009 Australian Open]], ampo i [[Victoria Azarenka]] king quarterfinals ning [[2012 Sony Ericsson Open]]. Simbut na la murin deng aliwang manimunang mamyalung anti di [[Venus Williams|Venus]] ampong [[Serena Williams]], [[Ana Ivanovic]], [[Lindsay Davenport]], [[Arantxa Sánchez Vicario]], [[Dinara Safina]], [[Caroline Wozniacki]], [[Petra Kvitová]], [[Samantha Stosur]] ampo i [[Kim Clijsters]]. 

Pikabalwan ya king kayang e karaniwan (''unorthodox'') a istilu ning pamamyalung a gagamit kareng adwang gamat king kayang forehand ampong backhand. Anyang 30 Enero 2012, disan ne ing pekamatas king kayang karera, a no. 7 king yatu. Miras ne i Bartoli por lo menos king quarter-final a dake ning balang metung kareng apat a Grand Slam. King kayang pamanyambut king Wimbledon, megi yang kanam a mamyalung king ''open era''ng e mesambut king sanumang set.<ref name="BBC Sport">BBC Sport (6 July 2013). [http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/tennis/23212453]</ref>

